query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.favorite_count >= 0 AND q.favorite_count <= 1
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('admob',
'asp-classic',
'azure-devops',
'cypher',
'deserialization',
'google-drive-api',
'gpu',
'icons',
'jsoup',
'microsoft-graph',
'rubygems',
'sql-server-2008-r2',
'statistics',
'time-complexity');
